      &lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;

&lt;!-- end snippet --&gt;


  [1]: https://stackoverflow.com/questions/14551305/align-attribute-deprecated
  [2]: https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Media_Queries/Using_media_queries

