To see the help for any magic command add a `?`: like `%loadpy?` or `%%writefile?`.&lt;br&gt;
`%COMMAND-NAME?`&lt;br&gt;
i.e. `%run?`&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;
For list of available magic function use `%lsmagic`.
